===Taskbot instance installation & settings===

For master host, please, read ../linux/README.

The project builds on master host (Ubuntu). Unit tests run on NX1 (bananian).

Prepare NX1:
 1. Prepare sdcard with valid version of image of the nx_vms:
   - https://networkoptix.atlassian.net/wiki/display/SD/How+to+get+clean+NX1+with+default+image.
 2. Set correct NX1 serial, mac and ip (NX1 shoud have internet access for the unit-tests):
   - https://networkoptix.atlassian.net/wiki/display/PM/Mac+Writer+Tool
 3. Prepare config_VERSION.py:
   - Set TASKBOT_NX1_ADDRESS variable
 4. Run ./prepare_nx1.sh script to create test user & copy ssh key.
